{"type": "article", "id": 22692, "title": "方糖沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-23T07:30:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021105461yAD98BklofRxzEa.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是有所推出的方糖沙发，与昨日推荐的布丁沙发一样带着食物的甜蜜。沙发的整体像一个立方体，四根白蜡木腿连接了靠背和很厚的方形座位，温和而静谧。设计者称选用的中性色和硬木颜色都是低存在感的颜色，希望带给人默默的关爱。售价 1019 元，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.1-c.w5003-11735453309.7.vtHuqk&amp;id=520444098938&amp;scene=taobao_shop\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110544HWvwcUrtpdJog5Z8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110544CzdQpUfg81asne6t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110544cpBS8KEbnryZiNC5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110545sdFHD0ZbELUOGwx9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110545kLXT4iNGBlaEgKYw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}